Request Dispatcher {forward(),include()}: 
It is an interface available in javax.servlet package.
It has two methods :
1.forward()
2.include()

Question: Difference between forward() and include()?

forward():forward() method is used to forward the request from -
          Servlet to HTML
          Servlet to JSP
          Servlet to Servlet
          JSP to HTML
          JSP to Servlet
          JSP to JSP
          
include():         



